---
title: Caramelized Pineapple Teriyaki Burger with Sweet Potatoe Wedges and Sriracha Mayo
description: Take your taste buds on a trip to the tropics! This recipe has warm and sunny flavors guaranteed to brighten up dinnertime. Teriyaki-glazed burgers are topped with charred onion slices and juicy, caramelized pineapple (aka happiness in a bun). On the side, there’s a heap of crispy sweet potato wedges and creamy sriracha mayo for dunking. Sweet, savory, and spicy--these bodacious burgers hit all the right notes. Plus, they’re a breeze to whip up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w14-r7-caramelized-pineapple-teriyaki-burger-18822721.jpg
